{"tid":2092702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羅冠聰確認離開香港","createTime":"2020-07-03T10:54:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T12:13:51.000Z","uid":60916,"like":5,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1ff294d6e94338196ddbd421403fc3bd3922219b","tid":2092702,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:54:06.000Z","msg":"《港區國安法》生效，退出香港眾志的羅冠聰周四（2日）晚上向傳媒確認，他已離開香港，會專注國際連結、民間外交工作，稱「基於風險評估」暫不便透露更多資訊。<br />\n<br />\n羅冠聰在facebook表示，港區國安法實施，「政權無法無天，以言入罪的情況已經發生」；他昨日（7月1日）在美國國會眾議院外交委員會的聽證會以網上遙距作證，「使自己陷入不可預知的危險之中」。他認為香港刻下必須捍衛國際戰線，稱在答應出席聽證會並決志日後承擔在散播港人抗爭意志的責任時，已有走到國際的準備。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">羅冠聰條契弟<br />\n一邊叫人上街抗國安法<br />\n另一邊就自己著草走人<br />\n同梁繼平有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n兩個都一早買定機票<br />\n一個叫人除罩留守立會<br />\n一個就叫人上街送頭</span></span>"},{"pid":"84361db0c59a7f6ce8bb8a5d55dcafe7d815184d","tid":2092702,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:54:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ad08f1225dd9dd095b1d8a30f69438f518ca15","tid":2092702,"uid":63822,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:54:31.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#60916 - 周俊樂(-10)</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請保持批判性思考，善用「上一頁」和「不推文回覆」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">該會員以往言論 (7)：</div><code>1 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/eQijrT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/eQijrT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠</span><br />\n<code>2 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/eBHfvT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/eBHfvT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠, 做假新聞</span><br />\n<code>3 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/eAEteT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/eAEteT</a><span style=\"color: red;\"></span><br />\n<code>4 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/esqExT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/esqExT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠</span><br />\n<code>5 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/esqBmT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/esqBmT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">洗白黑警</span><br />\n<code>6 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/epmkQT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/epmkQT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">藍屍言論</span><br />\n<code>7 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/epmfaT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/epmfaT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">藍屍言論</span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">「歷史回顧，無忘初心」</div><pre><code data-type=\"\">2019年9月22日\n和你shop 4.0</code></pre><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9t9fspu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9t9fspu.jpg&h=12ff2b6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"377584fac9d10fc82078d46f0b0199f7f53dc9dd","tid":2092702,"uid":30719,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:55:03.000Z","msg":"小心泛登仔屌返你轉頭"},{"pid":"8a3e0f4f81439d6abb9d481654e5103904815b12","tid":2092702,"uid":60916,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"377584fac9d10fc82078d46f0b0199f7f53dc9dd","tid":2092702,"uid":30719,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:55:03.000Z","msg":"小心泛登仔屌返你轉頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:55:37.000Z","msg":"開左三個<br />\n全部搬哂去政事"},{"pid":"25e5839fb284fae5047feb102333d6d090860b85","tid":2092702,"uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:56:36.000Z","msg":"現代孫中山 可敬"},{"pid":"0972dbfefad9b1733ccee28181b0cc6b5e8fe79b","tid":2092702,"uid":352564,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:57:16.000Z","msg":"樓主好落力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同我吠大聲D<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89ed7b9fbd7daa94bf725545b8d0454760a7b8c","tid":2092702,"uid":219156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"377584fac9d10fc82078d46f0b0199f7f53dc9dd","tid":2092702,"uid":30719,"like